children.name: PP-002 Sessions Details
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint 
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "mod=(?<module>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "rule=(?<rule>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| isEmpty(cmd) ? "system" : cmd as cmd

children.name: PP-003 Troubleshoot A Session
children.description: Key in a session ID to see all the logs relating to that session
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint KEY_IN_A_SESSION_HERE
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "mod=(?<module>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "rule=(?<rule>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| isEmpty(cmd) ? "system" : cmd as cmd

children.name: PP-004 Connection Orgins
children.description: Show the connection origin IPs and geo info.
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint connect
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "mod=(?<module>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "ip=(?<src_ip>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| where !(src_ip matches "127.0.0.1" or src_ip matches "10.*")
| lookup longitude,latitude,country_name,city from geo://default on src_ip=ip
| count src_ip, longitude, latitude, country_name, city
| sort _count

children.name: PP-005 Rejected Connection Orgins
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint (connect or disconnect)
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "ip=(?<src_ip>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "action=(?<action>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| join (where action="reject") as a, (where cmd="connect") as b on a.session=b.session
| fields b_src_ip, b_session
| where !(b_src_ip matches "127.0.0.1" or b_src_ip matches "10.*")
| lookup longitude,latitude,country_name,city from geo://default on b_src_ip=ip
| count b_session, b_src_ip, longitude, latitude, country_name, city
| sort _count

children.name: PP-006 Top Sender To Recipient
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint !reject (connect or disconnect or env_from or env_rcpt)
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "ip=(?<src_ip>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "value=(?<value>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "action=(?<action>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "m=(?<m>\d+?)\s" nodrop
| isEmpty(m) ? 0 : m as m
| (cmd="disconnect" and isEmpty(action)) ? "ok" : "bad" as action
| fields session, cmd, src_ip, value, action, m
| join (where action="ok") as a, (where cmd="connect") as b, (where cmd="env_from"|count session,m,value) as c, (where cmd="env_rcpt" | count session,m,value) as d on a.session=b.session and a.session=c.session and a.session=d.session and c.m=d.m
| c_value as sender
| d_value as recipient
| count b_src_ip, b_session, sender, recipient
| count sender, recipient | sort _count, recipient, sender

children.name: PP-007 Email Processing Performance
children.description: This can be used to alert on large email or long processed emails
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint disconnect "action= "
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "helo=(?<helo>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "msgs=(?<msgs>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "rcpts=(?<rcpts>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "duration=(?<duration>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "elapsed=(?<elapsed>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop

children.name: PP-008 Sessions With Long Duration
children.description: Tweak this to alert on abnormal sessions
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint !reject (disconnect or env_from or env_rcpt) 
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "value=(?<value>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "action=(?<action>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "msgs=(?<msgs>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "rcpts=(?<rcpts>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "duration=(?<duration>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "elapsed=(?<elapsed>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "m=(?<m>\d+?)\s" nodrop
| isEmpty(m) ? 0 : m as m
| (cmd="disconnect" and isEmpty(action)) ? "ok" : "bad" as action
| fields session, cmd, src_ip, value, action, msgs,rcpts,duration,elapsed,m
// find the transaction took more than 10 seconds
| join (where action="ok" and duration>10) as a, (where cmd="env_from"|count session,m,value) as c, (where cmd="env_rcpt" | count session,m,value) as d on a.session=c.session and a.session=d.session and c.m=d.m
| c_value as sender
| d_value as recipient
| count a_session, a_rcpts, sender, recipient, a_duration
| sort a_duration

children.name: PP-009 Subjects In The Email
children.description: Tweak this to alert on abnormal sessions
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint subject msg 
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "value=(?<value>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "action=(?<action>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "subject=(?:\"|)(?<subject>.*?)(?:\"|\s\w+=)" nodrop
| where !isEmpty(subject)
| count subject | sort _count

children.name: PP-010 Attachment Types
children.description: Can also be used to filter file name or by file size.
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint "cmd=attachment"
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "mod=(?<module>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "file=(?:\"|)(?<file>.*?)(?:\"|\s\w+=)" nodrop
| extract "size=(?<size>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "type=(?<type>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| isEmpty(cmd) ? "system" : cmd as cmd
| count type
| sort _count

panels.name: Commands
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| where !isEmpty(cmd)
| count cmd 
| sort _count

panels.name: Sessions With Long Duration
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint disconnect "action= " 
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "value=(?<value>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "action=(?<action>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "msgs=(?<msgs>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "rcpts=(?<rcpts>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop

| where duration>10
| count session, rcpts, duration | fields -_count 
| sort duration | limit 20

panels.name: Commands By Modules
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint 
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "mod=(?<module>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "rule=(?<rule>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| isEmpty(cmd) ? "system" : cmd as cmd
| count module,cmd
| transpose row cmd column module

panels.name: Most Frequent Subject
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint subject msg !"Out of Office"
| extract "s=(?<session>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "cmd=(?<cmd>\S+?)\s" nodrop
| extract "value=(?<value>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop
| extract "action=(?<action>\S*?)(?:\s|$)" nodrop 
| extract "subject=(?:\"|)(?<subject>.*?)(?:\"|\s\w+\=)" nodrop
| where !isEmpty(subject)
| count subject | sort _count | limit 20

panels.name: Sessions Handled Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$ProofPoint 
| parse "s=* " as session | timeslice 5m 
| count_distinct(session) as sessions by _timeslice
